This is a guide from
https://www.reddit.com/r/Gentoo/comments/150r74m/guide_hyprland_nvidia_extremely_minimal_gentoo/
where i have modified a little bit of it.

Follow the gentoo guide and guide on top to see when to enable these following

you need to remove gentoo repo "eselect repository remove gentoo && rm -rf /var/db/repos/gentoo"
you need to add gentoo git repo "eselect repository add gentoo git https://github.com/gentoo-mirror/gentoo.git"
repository to enable also "eselect repository enable wayland-desktop guru pf4public"
